#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;Adds additional color combinations to randomly generated weapons.^reset;

This sample shows the most basic way to add your own desired colors to the randomly generated weapons pool.
Requires Colorful Armory Tweaks Core NOT Basic.

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

